shape (super class)

Length (l)
Height (h)

→ Get user input (l, h)
→ Calculate perimeter (2l + 2h) 
→ Calculate area (l * h)
→ Constructor
→ Display results(area and perimeter)



Triangle (extends Shape)

Second side length (y)
Third side length (z)

→ Get user input (l, h, y, z) (override)
→ Constructor
→ Calculate perimeter (l + y + z)
→ Calculate area (l * h / 2)
→ Triangle type



Square (extends Shape)

→ get user input (l) (override)
→ Calculate area (l^2)
→ Calculate perimeter (4l)
→ Constructor
